to stay out of prison.

05:33.053 --> 05:34.896
That's a thousand years ago.

05:34.898 --> 05:36.741
Yeah, I figured.

05:39.072 --> 05:42.246
You still in touch
with any of the old crowd?

05:42.247 --> 05:43.749
Mike?

