05:54.015 --> 05:55.619
- He's not dead.
- Good.

05:55.620 --> 05:59.067
He's in a coma, up at grace.

05:59.068 --> 06:01.742
Pretty high mortality rate
in the old business.

06:04.497 --> 06:06.875
Gretchen'?

