that's a good memory.

07:46.530 --> 07:49.409
Been a long time.
More than 20 years.

07:49.410 --> 07:50.684
25.

07:50.685 --> 07:53.097
My mistake.

07:53.098 --> 07:54.941
A man does that kind
of hard time,

07:54.942 --> 07:57.445
you don't want to get
the numbers wrong.

08:00.447 --> 08:05.055
I can't blame you
for being suspicious.

08:05.056 --> 08:09.698
I mean, here I am,
sitting in the dark,

08:09.699 --> 08:11.178
waiting for you,

08:11.179 --> 08:14.649
what do you want from me,
Ethan?

08:14.650 --> 08:16.596
I just...

08:19.699 --> 08:21.700
I just want to buy you a drink.

08:43.923 --> 08:47.234
I got a 35% stake
in this place.

08:47.235 --> 08:48.578
Easy money.

08:48.579 --> 08:50.456
Kind of owe it
to you and my dad.

08:50.460 --> 08:55.409
My mom told me your big plan
was to cash out and open a club.

08:56.981 --> 08:58.585
